{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"74192979-fab6-4ad1-bb62-31d775f01ffb","content":"","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_vjbWzyI7ibY5LUYJmRBCo4","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Providing crash dump config"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"tooluse_T2O14Crd6i2Znqk9szCzOV","name":"bash","arguments":{"command":"echo \"Generating Kubernetes pod spec for NativeAOT crash dump collection\"","description":"Placeholder for context","initial_wait":10},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"Placeholder for context"}],"interactionId":"27f7b331-2f27-478b-b0c4-0d1e054de797","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user wants to configure automatic crash dump collection for a NativeAOT .NET 11 app running in Kubernetes. They have `createdump` installed at `/opt/tools/createdump`. I need to provide:\n\n1. The environment variables needed to configure .NET to use createdump for automatic crash dump collection\n2. The Kubernetes pod spec changes needed\n\nFor .NET NativeAOT apps, crash dump collection works differently than regular CoreCLR. Let me think about what's needed:\n\nFor .NET (especially NativeAOT), the relevant environment variables are:\n- `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump=1` - enables mini dump collection on crash\n\n\n- `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType` - controls the dump format (1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage, 4=Full)\n- `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName` - specifies where to save the dump file\n- `DOTNET_CreateDumpDiagnostics` - enables diagnostics output from createdump\n- `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` - points to the createdump executable since it's in a non-standard location\n\nFor NativeAOT, createdump support is available in .NET 8 and later, so I need to check if .NET 11 supports this or if there's a different approach needed.\n\nFor Kubernetes deployment, I'll need to configure environment variables in the container spec, set up a volume mount for storing dumps, and potentially add `SYS_PTRACE` capability in the security context since createdump requires elevated permissions to attach to processes.","outputTokens":571,"requestId":"6815:1F9E71:C6B0BC:D41F84:6A0B0097"},"id":"18789206-11f6-4312-8d4b-4483b96dcaff","timestamp":"2026-05-18T12:05:56.120Z","parentId":"014e6c57-2026-42a4-825e-8266d3eaf3f9"}
